  "keywords": "Gujarat industrial technologies 2026, industrial automation Gujarat, AI in manufacturing India, IoT smart factories Gujarat, CNC machine tools Gujarat, additive manufacturing India, renewable energy manufacturing, digital twin technology",
  "url": "https://engitechexpo.com/gujarat-industrial-tech-2026-trends-guide/",
